-75525656.text: "Selective targeting of the IGF signaling network has proven to be extremely challenging due, in part, to the fact that insulin, IGF-1 and IGF-2 can all activate IGF-1-R and/or IGF-2R, as well as the insulin receptor (XREF_FIG)."
